name: RAD-ISH
description:
Rude Veggies is a collection of 10 radical characters, inspired in the vegetables lovers and my childhood imagination. Full of colors, funny outfits, cool hobbies and tons of good vibes! 

Rad-ish, is the 2nd character, He is part of the team, a stylish folk who likes to chill with his friend and wear neat sneakers. 

He is ready to meet new collectors.


Drawing by MNNLLIA
2021
